serif\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-size:17px\"><em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"color:#222222\">- Xếp nốt phần m&igrave; c&ograve;n lại l&ecirc;n l&agrave; ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh.</span></span></em></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-size:17px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">Vậy l&agrave; ch&uacute;ng ta đ&atilde; c&oacute; một chiếc burger m&igrave; g&oacute;i kẹp thịt rồi n&agrave;y. Cắt đ&ocirc;i chiếc burger m&igrave; g&oacute;i n&agrave;y ra v&agrave; thưởng thức ngay n&agrave;o!</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"GifPhoto VCSortableInPreviewMode active noCaption\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; border:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:22px; margin-right:22px; margin-top:0px; padding:0px; text-align:center; width:580px\">\r\n<div class=\"gifPaused media-wrapper\" style=\"border:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:0px; padding:0px\">\r\n<div class=\"media-status\" style=\"border:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:0px; padding:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:17px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-size:11px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Arial\"><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)\"><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><strong>GIF</strong><span style=\"background-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2)\"><span style=\"color:transparent\">.</span></span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active noCaption\"